  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to investigate whether a predictive score (combination of several
      validated predictors) better predicts postoperative left ventricular function than any single
      predictor in patients undergoing mitral valve repair for degenerative mitral regurgitation.

      A single center, prospective cohort study
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
