      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion criteria:

          -  Age 18- 85 years

          -  Patients with severe degenerative mitral regurgitation undergoing mitral valve repair
             at our institution

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  Functional or ischemic mitral regurgitation

          -  Presence of relevant (symptomatic) Coronary Artery Disease

          -  Inability of exercising on semi supine bicycle
      </textblock>
